 og en halv million kroner. Det er un\u00f8dvendig, mener Knobloch."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "24a705c90580fb218f2253d0037e73681fdfd955beb833e688dc6882052272b7"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T15:32:01.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Syklister mener det saltes for mye i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13888406.ece/xiv3q5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/doc6sn8aop6umx1c3iot3fc.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d70e2e71192631649a5bdd56041f80583aaee599.jpg?5994a489"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Saltet \u00f8delegger syklene og vinterf\u00f8ret -adressa.no", "Vil sykle p\u00e5 sn\u00f8", "Diskusjonstema", "Syklene ruster", "62 kjedebrudd", "Bar-vei-standard", "Mange henvendelser", "Kostbart vedlikehold"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "d70e2e71192631649a5bdd56041f80583aaee599"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["sykkel", "vintervedlikehold"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "sykkel,vintervedlikehold"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "hobbies-and-interests"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["saltet \u00f8delegger syklene", "salt", "sykle", "\u00f8delegger syklene"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["bakklandet", "st. olavs", "knobloch", "by\u00e5sen", "ceciliebrua", "milj\u00f8pakken", "\u00f8ye", "christian \u00f8ye og rainer knobloch", "sykkelbua"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["ivar arne devik", "christian \u00f8ye", "rainer knobloch", "morten b\u00f8stein-melhus"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/